title: Sample Book, Glengary, 1963
description: Patterns simulating silks, moires, brocatelles, each in multiple colorways. Also includes Italian marble and metallic papers.  Many samples of plain ground colors in the back of book.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Glengary, 1963; Manufactured by Imperial Wallcoverings, Inc. (United States); USA; paper, acrylic coated, embossed; Overall: 30.5 x 23 x 3 cm (12 x 9 1/16 x 1 3/16 in.); Gift of Various Donors; 1980-78-11-1/102
